{"tid":2202523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Podcast主持人提議幫侵同拜登主持一場4小時閉門辯論 侵話無問題","createTime":"2020-09-14T15:26:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T16:32:07.000Z","uid":270889,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c0dfb5044fd143b2dc02a2e28923fa8de6bd86df","tid":2202523,"uid":270889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T15:26:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1305487258036781056?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1305487258036781056%3Fs%3D20&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=cf7094f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FrealDonaldTrump%2Fstatus%2F1305487258036781056%3Fs%3D20&h=dfd039bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/realDonaldTrump/status/1305487258036781056?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\nPresident Trump on Monday jumped on an offer from mixed martial arts commentator and Spotify podcast host Joe Rogan to moderate a <span class=\"red\">four-hour debate</span> with former Vice President Joe Biden.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I do,&rdquo; Trump responded on Twitter to a post from Tim Kennedy, a retired MMA fighter.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;On my podcast with @joerogan he offered to moderate a debate between @JoeBiden and @realDonaldTrump It would be <span class=\"red\">four hours with no live audience</span>. <span class=\"red\">Just the two candidates, cameras, and their vision of how to move this country forward.</span> Who wants this?&rdquo; Kennedy said in his tweet.<br />\n<br />\nRogan and Kennedy were discussing the debates Sunday on the podcast &ldquo;The Joe Rogan Experience.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;But <span class=\"red\">I don&rsquo;t think that Biden can handle</span> it. I think Biden is like, I think he&rsquo;s, I mean people get mad at me for saying this, I think there&rsquo;s something wrong and I don&rsquo;t think there&rsquo;s something wrong, because I&rsquo;m guessing, or because I&rsquo;m pro-Trump. I&rsquo;ve seen him fall apart,&rdquo; Rogan said.<br />\n<br />\nThe two candidates have agreed to three debates with the moderators selected by the Commission on Presidential Debates.<br />\n<br />\nThe first debate will be held Sept. 29 in Cleveland, the second Oct. 15 in Miami and the third Oct. 22 in Nashville.<br />\n<br />\nThe moderators are Kristen Welker of NBC News, Steve Scully, the political editor of C-SPAN Networks, and Chris Wallace of Fox News.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nypost.com/2020/09/14/trump-accepts-offer-from-joe-rogan-to-moderate-debate-with-biden/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2020%2F09%2F14%2Ftrump-accepts-offer-from-joe-rogan-to-moderate-debate-with-biden%2F&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=6181dd0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nypost.com/2020/09/14/trump-accepts-offer-from-joe-rogan-to-moderate-debate-with-biden/</a>"},{"pid":"3656c2cc57fd1038202f8456a33841a830925cd9","tid":2202523,"uid":224533,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T15:27:31.000Z","msg":"閉門辯論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有乜撚野用呀"},{"pid":"a012fbe17364d481ff5bf55cffcd3c78707eb4e3","tid":2202523,"uid":270889,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"3656c2cc57fd1038202f8456a33841a830925cd9","tid":2202523,"uid":224533,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T15:27:31.000Z","msg":"閉門辯論<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有乜撚野用呀"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T15:29:26.000Z","msg":"閉門開門都殺啦<br />\n閉門又唔係唔廣播<br />\n我想睇呀糟點頂4 hours呀<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/KamVTV/status/1305515519949393926?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKamVTV%2Fstatus%2F1305515519949393926%3Fs%3D20&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacSKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=1ce4afee\" data-ef-url=\"ht